{"tid":1630873,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"武磊參加7場西甲0入球0助攻，愛斯賓奴難求一勝，唯獨武磊缺席的那場，愛斯賓奴勝利","createTime":"2019-10-06T13:58:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T14:10:25.000Z","uid":173952,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a785e557cfa27490a80283b1a31f4edbfd6776de","tid":1630873,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:58:41.000Z","msg":"新賽季西甲已經踢了8場，武磊至今顆粒無收，他依然在苦苦尋求自己的第一粒西甲入球。<br />\n  今季愛斯賓奴的8場比賽，武磊參加了7場，其中5場比賽正選出場，總出場時間425分鐘，平均每場出場60.7分鐘。<br />\n  武磊在這425分鐘的出場時間里，沒有入球，也沒有助攻，新賽季的西甲賽場，他依然遭遇球荒。武磊參加的這7場比賽，他一共射門9次，射正僅僅2次，射正率僅為22.2%。<br />\n  尷尬的是，武磊參加的這7場比賽，愛斯賓奴難求一勝，唯獨武磊缺席的那場比賽，愛斯賓奴取得了勝利。西甲第4輪，愛斯賓奴作客2-1擊敗埃瓦爾，當時武磊坐在後備席沒有出場。<br />\n<br />\n為左支那市場,明知廢仲要死出佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5分排緊19位,再出佢真係會降班<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a9e013d11d4585eba9e7bca96ff36b4ba3dc028","tid":1630873,"uid":34952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:01:29.000Z","msg":"歐霸入波有排佢地J啦<br />\n西甲降班WFC"},{"pid":"39a2af24c062664e5948b3b2739d5f1ec7872210","tid":1630873,"uid":192409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:02:34.000Z","msg":"上季季中加盟好似好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c4854699b66c4c24f88f035f7b2068df94802f2","tid":1630873,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"39a2af24c062664e5948b3b2739d5f1ec7872210","tid":1630873,"uid":192409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:02:34.000Z","msg":"上季季中加盟好似好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:03:06.000Z","msg":"虛火"},{"pid":"e2c2ded60ce39d2a2f1a54c0923